    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      104.78,
      445.0,
      526.11,
      458.28
    ],
    "text": "an offence punishable under Section 317 of the Penal Code. However, at the",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      104.78,
      465.78,
      526.09,
      479.06
    ],
    "text": "conclusion of the trial, the learned High Court Judge found the appellant guilty of",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      104.78,
      486.42,
      526.1,
      499.7
    ],
    "text": "causing simple hurt and accordingly convicted him under Section 315 of the Penal",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      104.78,
      507.18,
      443.5,
      520.46
    ],
    "text": "Code, as the evidence did not support a conviction under Section 317.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      86.78,
      548.41,
      526.12,
      561.86
    ],
    "text": "2. The learned High Court Judge sentenced the appellant to two years' rigorous",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      104.78,
      569.22,
      526.06,
      582.5
    ],
    "text": "imprisonment, suspended for five years. A fine of Rs. 7,500.00 was also imposed, with",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      104.78,
      589.98,
      526.11,
      603.26
    ],
    "text": "a default sentence of six months. Furthermore, the learned High Court Judge ordered",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      104.78,
      610.62,
      526.09,
      623.9
    ],
    "text": "the appellant to pay the victim Rs. 500,000.00 as compensation, failing which he shall",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      104.78,
      631.38,
      350.35,
      644.66
    ],
    "text": "serve a further six months' rigorous imprisonment.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      86.78,
      652.05,
      526.05,
      681.17
    ],
    "text": "3. In the petition of appeal, the appellant initially sought to have the conviction and",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      104.78,
      688.65,
      526.04,
      701.93
    ],
    "text": "sentence quashed and to be acquitted of the charge. Nonetheless, at the hearing of the",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      104.78,
      709.29,
      526.05,
      722.57
    ],
    "text": "appeal, the court was informed that the appellant would only contest the sentence. The",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      104.78,
      730.05,
      526.09,
      743.33
    ],
    "text": "appellant prayed that the fine imposed be converted to State costs, so that, as a",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      266.21,
      36.28,
      334.48,
      45.18
    ],
