    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      90.02,
      212.53,
      529.35,
      241.65
    ],
    "text": "5. When a request is made for a reduction of sentence, the Court is required to carefully",
    "fonts": [
      "ArialMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
