    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      249.13,
      529.61,
      262.41
    ],
    "text": "consider both the aggravating and mitigating factors present in the case. At the time of",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      269.8,
      529.33,
      283.08
    ],
    "text": "the incident, the appellant was a school teacher attached to the Kebithigollewa",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      290.56,
      529.33,
      303.84
    ],
    "text": "Education Office as an instructor. The victim, who suffered from epilepsy, had sought",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
